text: Makuch or Macuch, or the alternatives Makúch and Macúch are surnames. Makuch and alternatives may refer to: ==Makuch== *Dirk Schulze-Makuch (born 1964), professor at the Center for Astronomy and Astrophysics *Jozef Makúch (born 1953), Slovak banker *Marcin Makuch (born 1980), Polish footballer *Wanda Makuch-Korulska (1919-2007), Polish medical doctor, specialist in neurology ==Macuch== *Rudolf Macúch (1919-1993) Slovakian and German linguist
title: Makuch
